Validic,helps,healthcare,businesses,connect,with,dozens,of,mobile,health,applications,apps,such,as,Fitbit,RunKeeper,MapMyRide,and,iHealth,and,offer,them,to,their,users,When,end,users,enter,data,into,an,app,that,data,gets,sent,to,the,healthcare,business,s,system,This,allows,the,business,to,collect,useful,information,from,their,customers,and,improve,their,healthcare,services,without,incurring,the,cost,of,developing,and,maintaining,their,own,system,of,app,connections,Integration,with,Validic,is,accomplished,using,its,RESTful,API